Dependencies:
    OpenCV development headers and libraries (http://opencv.willowgarage.com/wiki/)

Compiling:
    make

Usage:
    Options:
        -o: Specify output directory. Default is "."
        -p: Specify output image prefix. Default is "spr_"
        -f: Specify output image format. Default is "png"

    Arguments:
        image file

    Example:
        ./spritecutter images/dbz.png -o ./output/ -p spr_        
        or
        ./spritecutter <image>

Thanks to:
    OpenCV for the image framework
        http://opencv.willowgarage.com/wiki/)
    CvBlob for the blob extraction algorithm and interface
        http://code.google.com/p/cvblob/
